MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2010-1892. Szerszen v. Summit Chase Condominiums.

Franklin App. No. 09AP-1183, 2010-Ohio-4518. This cause is pending before the court as a discretion*1492ary appeal. Upon consideration of appellants’ application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
